<h1>Users</h1>
<p>The user list is split into three categories:</p>
<ul>
	<li>ACTIVE: Users who can use the system</li>
	<li>BLOCKED: Users who are temporarily blocked from using the system</li>
	<li>DELETED: Users who have been deleted.</li>
</ul>
<p>Once a user has been created, their account will remain in the system to ensure that historical data is maintained.</p>
<h2>New user</h2>
<ul>
	<li>Click <em>New user</em> to create a new user.</li>
</ul>
<h4>Further help</h4>
<p><a href="#" data-page="2">New user</a><br>
