<ul>
	<li>First name: enter the first name of the user (compulsory)</li>
	<li>Last name: enter the last name of the user (compulsory)</li>
	<li>Email address: enter the email address of the user (compulsory)</li>
	<li>Template for welcome email: choose to automatically send a welcome email to the new user with a link for them to create their own password. If you choose to not send a welcome email, you will be given a link to send to the new user once you click on <em>Create new user</em>.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
	<li>Group membership: tick all groups to which the user is to belong</li>
	<li><em>Create new user</em>.</li>
