	<li><em>Group membership</em>: The groups the user belongs to.</li>
	<li><em>Permissions</em>: The effective permissions for this user, taking into account all the permissions for the groups the user belongs to. Note that permissions are usually set on groups, so editing a user&#8217;s permissions usually make no statement on their permissions.</li>
	<li><em>Latest updates</em>: (may be renamed) Adjust the latest updates settings, including email frequency.</li>
