<p><a href="#" data-page="19">Type information</a><br>
<a href="#" data-page="20">Edit types</a><br>
<a href="#" data-page="21">Attributes</a></p>
</div>

<div id="p19" style="display:none">
<h1>Type information</h1>
<p>This shows information about the selected type.</p>
