<div id="p53" style="display:none">
<h1>Email templates</h1>
<p>Email templates allow you to customise the emails sent by PRODUCT_NAME. You need knowledge of HTML and CSS to edit these templates, and it&#8217;s recommended you seek the assistance of a designer to get the best results.</p>
<h2>Edit an email template</h2>
