	<li>Choose the email template from the list and click on <em>Remove from menu</em> in the right hand panel.</li>
</ul>
<p>Removing a template from the menu stops it being selected in the future. The template will still be used if currently selected for any feature, removing it from the menu marks it as not intended for use.</p>
<h2>Restore to menu</h2>
<ul>
	<li>Choose the email template from the list and click on <em>Restore to menu</em> in the right hand panel.</li>
