	<li><em>From (name)</em>: the name shown in the from field of the email</li>
	<li><em>Extra CSS</em>: Additional CSS included in the HTML, to customise the look of the email.</li>
	<li><em>Branding (plain)</em>: Text which appears at the top of the plain text version of this email. Use the interpolated strings listed above where required.</li>
	<li><em>Branding (HTML)</em>: HTML which appears at the top of the HTML version of this email. Use the interpolated strings listed above where required.</li>
